race.comment: PRINCE RAGNAR (3) is bursting to win and this looks his moment. Has placed in all but one run this prep and went down narrowly here last time after giving his all. Loves racing at this track and the claim gets him in beautifully at the weights. Everything points to him going one better. BIGDAYONIT (6) is racing much better than it reads on paper. Stuck on well at Belmont over further and now drops back to a trip that suits. Maps kindly and looks a genuine threat. SNIPPY WHICH (2) flashed home to grab PRINCE RAGNAR last time and clearly enjoys this circuit. Could be an awkward draw for him but hard to leave out given his strong finish. THEHORSEMAN (4) returned in top order with a dominant display here. Slight query second up but must be respected. BE SEATED (5) resumes and always tries hard. Worth keeping in mind for multiples.
